Description: Open creativity lab at the Bellevue Library. Come experiment, imagine, play, problem solve & explore using a variety of creative tools, materials, software programs & more. Meet other makers and creatives to build community connections & learn together. This is a BYOI space--Bring Your Own Ideas.Some featured creative tools are: Lego Mindstorms, Little Bits, Play-Doh, Makey-Makey, 3Doodler Pens, Stop-Motion Animation Kits, the Adobe Creative Suite and Ableton Live software + Ableton Push.
Title: ideaX Drop-in Creativity Lab
